subject: Football
College Athletics
organizations: Rutgers, The State University of New Jersey
lead_paragraph: Two weeks ago, Cincinnati was one of the most surprising teams in the nation, undefeated and thinking about championships. After a 24-17 loss at Pittsburgh yesterday, the No. 23 Bearcats are tied for last place in the Big East.
